- all markdown documents must have YAML frontmatter
    - required fields: id, title, status, date, author
    - id format: UUID v4 (uppercase with hyphens)
    - status: Valid "Status Enum Value"
    - date format: YYYY-MM-DD
    - optional fields:
      - related (array of UUIDs)
      - children (array of UUIDs)
    - see 528D3D34-4750-408B-85F7-EF910ED87DA2 for complete specification
    - author: must be a list
        - ex: <git config user.name> (<git config user.email>)
        - ex: AI Assistant (<Model Used>)
